observations.recommendation:
We recommend that management submit the following:
a.Report on Sources and Utilization of LDRRMF on or before the 15th day after the end of each month to the COA auditor of the LGU;
b.Lacking documentation for the disbursement amounting to ₱365,000.00; 
c.Disbursement Voucher for the purchase of NFA Rice amounting to ₱187,500.00; and 
d.Liquidation Report for the cash advance amounting to ₱100,000.00 taken from the 30% quick response fund.

Furthermore, we recommend that management observe the accounting and reporting guidelines set forth under COA Circular No. 2012-002 by following the prescribed format in disclosing the amount allocated for MOOE and Capital Outlay.
